# UnrealCodex - Codex Instructions for Unreal Engine 5.7

This is a Codex-branded template for project guidance.

## Important

- Runtime context loading in this plugin currently reads `CLAUDE.md` for compatibility.
- Use this file as a template, then copy to `CLAUDE.md` in your project/plugin root.

## Quick Setup

1. Copy `CODEX.md.default` to `CLAUDE.md`
2. Fill in your local paths and project rules
3. Keep it concise and project-specific

For the full guidance template, use `CLAUDE.md.default` in the same directory.
